{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbc6d8ceb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s3108"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3108"},"text":"§ 3108.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbc6d8cec-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s3108/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" There are authorized to be appropriated for each fiscal year commencing after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1965","children":[],"tail":", and ending prior to "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1969-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1969","children":[],"tail":", not to exceed (1) $200,000,000 (or $350,000,000 in the case of the fiscal year commencing "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1968","children":[],"tail":") for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3102"},"text":"section 3102 of this title","children":[],"tail":", (2) $50,000,000 for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3103"},"text":"section 3103 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and (3) $25,000,000 for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3104"},"text":"section 3104 of this title","children":[],"tail":". In addition, there is authorized to be appropriated for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3102"},"text":"section 3102 of this title","children":[],"tail":" not to exceed $115,000,000 for the fiscal year commencing "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1969-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1969","children":[],"tail":", and not to exceed $100,000,000 for the fiscal year commencing "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1970","children":[],"tail":". In addition, upon the enactment of the Emergency Community Facilities Act of 1970, there is authorized to be appropriated for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3102"},"text":"section 3102 of this title","children":[],"tail":" not to exceed $1,000,000,000 for the fiscal year commencing "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1970","children":[],"tail":". In addition, there is authorized to be appropriated for the fiscal year commencing "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1971-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1971","children":[],"tail":", not to exceed $50,000,000 for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3103"},"text":"section 3103 of this title","children":[],"tail":". In addition, there are authorized to be appropriated for the fiscal year commencing "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1973","children":[],"tail":", not to exceed $40,000,000 for grants under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3103"},"text":"section 3103 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbc6d8ced-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s3108/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Any amounts appropriated under this section shall remain available until expended, and any amounts authorized for any fiscal year under this section but not appropriated may be appropriated for any succeeding fiscal year commencing prior to ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1974","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbc6d8cee-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/117/tVII/s708"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–117, title VII, § 708","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-08-10"},"text":"Aug. 10, 1965","children"